练习内容

创建数据库并创建测试表
获取数据库条目内容
向数据库中插入一条内容
删除一条数据
支持命令行方式
必要的错误处理

$ python database.py get
+----+------+----------------------+----------+
| id | name | email                | password |
+----+------+----------------------+----------+
| 1  | bqi  | bqi@hillstonenet.com | abcd1234 |
+----+------+----------------------+----------+
$ python database.py insert
name: hillstone
email: hillstone@hillstonenet.com
password: hillstone

Insert successfully.
$ python database.py delete
Please input the id: 1

Success to delete the item: id=1
